Usage
Login with default credentials (admin/123)

Configure your shop settings

Add items with their cost, margin, quantity, etc.

View real-time calculations

Generate and print bills

Access history and export data as needed

Technologies Used
HTML5

CSS3 (with animations and 3D transforms)

JavaScript (ES6)

QRCode.js for UPI QR generation

LocalStorage for data persistence

Font Awesome for icons

Google Fonts (Poppins)

